data.description: **PRICE IMPROVED ** Welcome to your dream retreat, this charming single family home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and over 1,700 square feet nestled in the heart of nature's tranquility.    Situated on an oversized corner lot at walking distance of Rainbow River. This home offers a unique chance to enjoy both ample outdoor space and cozy indoor.  The lush green surroundings ensure privacy while allowing you to relish the beauty of nature.    Endless opportunities to explore the outdoors! Immerse yourself in the nice trails, lush parks, and untouched nature preserves that bring you a sense of peace and connection.    One of the highlights is the property's proximity to Rainbow River. Rainbow river is formed by a first-magnitude spring, ranked fourth in the state for volume of discharge  400-600 million gallons of crystalline water every day. It is also a popular destination to swim, snorkel, canoe, picnic, or stroll on the walking paths to enjoy the many plants and animals that abound here.Its calm waters, springs, and vibrant surroundings make it a perfect spot for Airbnb or vacation rental, inviting guests to experience the magic of the area.
